==English==
===Noun===
'''civvy street'''
# A term used in the uniformed services (e.g. Army, Police) to describe life beyond the service; "civvy" being a corruption of the word "civilian".  This term has a temporal sense (i.e. one's life before or after uniformed service) as well as a geographic sense (i.e. the places one habituates when not in the uniformed service).